languages around the house.

1059
00:56:06.906 --> 00:56:10.366
Okay. I am on the phone.
We can see that. right?

1060
00:56:10.367 --> 00:56:11.701
Do we know phone.

1061
00:56:11.702 --> 00:56:13.912
or do I need to tattoo it
on my fucking forehead?

1062
