to Cambodia.

1081
00:57:05.714 --> 00:57:07.298
Then there's my Uncle McArthur.

1082
00:57:07.299 --> 00:57:09.050
Sir. you've got about
a 30-knot wind

1083
00:57:09.051 --> 00:57:10.718
