1104
00:57:54.972 --> 00:57:58.808
Charlie 17.
you are very low. over.

1105
00:57:59.810 --> 00:58:03.188
1.500 square feet.
three bedrooms. doorman.

1106
00:58:03.189 --> 00:58:05.481
You ever have a doorman before?

1107
00:58:05.482 --> 00:58:07.358
