Nice office you got here.

1170
01:01:27.684 --> 01:01:29.727
I like it.

1171
01:01:29.728 --> 01:01:30.812
Just so we understand.

1172
01:01:30.813 --> 01:01:32.063
you said you're not an heir

1173
01:01:32.064 --> 01:01:33.232
