- He invited me.

1241
01:05:51.615 --> 01:05:52.741
What?

1242
01:05:53.450 --> 01:05:55.409
My grandfather.

1243
01:05:55.410 --> 01:05:58.080
To a dinner party at the estate.

1244
01:05:59.289 --> 01:06:01.332
- Hello?
- Uh. I just...

1245
01:06:01.333 --> 01:06:03.918
I... I thought you said
